as we get a fix on her.

159
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,833
Trust me, Jo; just do
as I say until then.

160
00:13:29,916 --> 00:13:31,083
That was our agreement.

161
00:13:31,166 --> 00:13:34,500
