187
00:14:50,458 --> 00:14:53,625
Not to worry. I'll mobilize
the entire Organization.

188
00:14:53,708 --> 00:14:56,250
We'll scour all of Tokyo
and the surrounding areas.

189
00:14:56,333 --> 00:14:57,958
