218
00:18:27,250 --> 00:18:28,958
Nanobot?

219
00:18:29,041 --> 00:18:31,333
They call it the NI-50.

220
00:18:31,416 --> 00:18:33,208
It's an array of
microscopic machines

221
00:18:33,291 --> 00:18:36,041
that kill you from
the inside out.

222
00:18:36,125 --> 00:18:38,208
Once injected,
it mutates your DNA

223
00:18:38,291 --> 00:18:40,500
and within six hours,
you will be dead.

224
00:18:40,583 --> 00:18:41,875
