so I can go fight that crow.

254
00:21:00,666 --> 00:21:03,250
I don't give a damn
about anyone but Meg.

255
00:21:03,333 --> 00:21:06,458
If you try to run,
I'll kill you.

256
00:21:11,166 --> 00:21:13,583
Attention all Tokyo Units!
All points bulletin!

257
00:21:13,666 --> 00:21:14,791
All units assist

258
00:21:14,875 --> 00:21:17,083
in the apprehension of
an 18 year-old male.

259
00:21:20,875 --> 00:21:22,416
Suspect is reported
to be traveling

260
00:21:22,500 --> 00:21:24,041
with an 18 year-old female.

261
00:21:24,125 --> 00:21:27,000
The female is to be considered
armed and extremely dangerous.

262
00:21:28,333 --> 00:21:31,625
Use of lethal force in their
apprehension has been approved.

263
00:21:43,583 --> 00:21:47,166
Less than six hours left
until the NI-50 takes over.

264
00:21:48,875 --> 00:21:53,291
Jo, you stupid, stupid girl.
You can't do this on your own.

265
00:21:53,375 --> 00:21:56,250
And now, you've made it
so I can't help you either.

266
00:22:15,583 --> 00:22:19,375
I don't know why I can't move

267
00:22:19,458 --> 00:22:23,250
My mind is lost in this cloud

268
00:22:23,333 --> 00:22:30,625
No one even hears my voice
and my tears fall to the ground

269
00:22:30,708 --> 00:22:38,250
It's like my feelings of
loneliness are falling too

270
00:22:38,333 --> 00:22:43,541
The truth is that we
all just want to smile

271
00:22:43,625 --> 00:22:47,708
and smile with each other

272
00:22:47,791 --> 00:22:51,000
It hurts inside
when we don't...

273
00:22:51,083 --> 00:22:54,625
we don't... we don't
know what to say

274
00:22:54,708 --> 00:22:59,375
I only hope that
someone will be there,

275
00:22:59,458 --> 00:23:03,458
and be watching over me

276
00:23:03,541 --> 00:23:05,458
so take my hand,

277
00:23:05,541 --> 00:23:14,250
we'll walk tonight
underneath the sky

278
00:23:32,125 --> 00:23:34,750
Traps set all over the
late-night metropolis

279
00:23:34,833 --> 00:23:38,541
attack with a snarl,
and Jo races against time!

280
00:23:38,625 --> 00:23:41,083
Will Kyo and Meg survive?

281
00:23:41,166 --> 00:23:45,375
Next Burst Angel:
The Wounded Fugitive.

